{"tid":2096511,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"国安法：無需陪審團   熱狗：挽回司法公正，建議區院引入陪審團","createTime":"2020-07-06T07:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T06:49:06.000Z","uid":7439,"like":22,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"710139d439993962c7ed5be932d920192331fcf9","tid":2096511,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/106543964_1170354576655282_5206699831670411229_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=6hYlMJitkyQAX8wnUou&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=6277ab0d9b038e85855a7f55f485e1d7&amp;oe=5F266874\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F106543964_1170354576655282_5206699831670411229_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3D6hYlMJitkyQAX8wnUou%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D6277ab0d9b038e85855a7f55f485e1d7%26oe%3D5F266874&h=b59d84e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/105977332_1170228943334512_8840309750333535113_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=gV0tFUa1Am0AX9WM5hI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=5fadf846d57be31459e9aefc413279a8&amp;oe=5F27AF0D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F105977332_1170228943334512_8840309750333535113_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DgV0tFUa1Am0AX9WM5hI%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D5fadf846d57be31459e9aefc413279a8%26oe%3D5F27AF0D&h=414b1a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃兆健 Siu-Kin Wong<br />\n昨天 10:10 發佈 &middot; <br />\n【#熱血公民新界東黃兆健團隊<br />\n「挽回司法公正 區院引入陪審團」街站時間表（5/7）】<br />\n<br />\n熱血公民新界東黃兆健團隊，今周將於新界東各區，設立街站，派發「挽回司法公正 區院引入陪審團」單張，講解熱血公民的司法改革倡議。<br />\n<br />\n自反修例運動於去年爆發以來，不少抗爭者遭濫捕濫告，法院就各宗政治案件的判決亦因而受到大眾關注。<span style=\"color: gold;\">當中有不少由區域法院審理的案件，因個別法官的政治取向、法庭對證詞的接受程度，以及量刑標準等，引起輿論對區域法院公正程度的譁聲。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">因此，我們建議於區域法院引入陪審團制度，避免法官個人的價值取向主導其判決之餘，亦確保判刑上限及定罪率高的區域法院，能作出公正的裁決。</span>此舉不但可保障被告的權益，更能挽回香港日漸淪喪的司法制度。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/106393902_1170982653259141_2696337080333762860_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=MVow0lzHyCgAX9Zzh77&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=f70426694fb17be5d20bf589e4a612ae&amp;oe=5F28E2A6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F106393902_1170982653259141_2696337080333762860_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DMVow0lzHyCgAX9Zzh77%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3Df70426694fb17be5d20bf589e4a612ae%26oe%3D5F28E2A6&h=5bbc9468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/106508085_1170982659925807_7495625603830738394_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=SA2JORe9TvIAX-nL3vY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=690caaa0ab35d2d944eace73ea8c0f80&amp;oe=5F268D5B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F106508085_1170982659925807_7495625603830738394_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DSA2JORe9TvIAX-nL3vY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D690caaa0ab35d2d944eace73ea8c0f80%26oe%3D5F268D5B&h=64eaa410&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/79230099_1170982693259137_5296408363094877768_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=3hUQrqzuP-AAX8vgYyo&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=b7f3914fb442e9979c38df5345cbab76&amp;oe=5F286441\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F79230099_1170982693259137_5296408363094877768_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3D3hUQrqzuP-AAX8vgYyo%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Db7f3914fb442e9979c38df5345cbab76%26oe%3D5F286441&h=36e88f6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b4501cf2aa61d8f6171d9f84483d2c412d52230","tid":2096511,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:18:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20202444e/cs220202444136.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gld.gov.hk%2Fegazette%2Fpdf%2F20202444e%2Fcs220202444136.pdf&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FqooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=c81424a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20202444e/cs220202444136.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n法官777欽點喎<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: gold;\">防止因個別法官的政治取向引起輿論？？？？？？？</span></ins><br />\n<blockquote><em>第四十四條 <span style=\"color: red;\">香港特別行政區行政長官</span>應當從裁判官、區域法院法官、高等法院原訟法庭法官、上訴法庭法官以及終審法院法官中<span style=\"color: red;\">指定若干名法官，也可從暫委或者特委法官中指定若干名法官，負責處理危害國家安全犯罪案件。</span>行政長官在指定法官前可徵詢香港特別行政區維護國家安全委員會和終審法院首席法官的意見。上述指定法官任期一年。<br />\n凡有危害國家安全言行的，不得被指定為審理危害國家安全犯罪案件的法官。在獲任指定法官期間，如有危害國家安全言行的，終止其指定法官資格。在裁判法院、區域法院、高等法院和終審法院就危害國家安全犯罪案件提起的刑事檢控程序應當分別由各該法院的指定法官處理。</em></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌，都話唔撚洗陪審團</span></span><br />\n要陪審團777欽點三個法官咪得<br />\n<blockquote><em>第四十六條 對高等法院原訟法庭進行的就危害國家安全犯罪案件提起的刑事檢控程序，律政司長可基於保護國家秘密、案件具有涉外因素或者保障陪審員及其家人的人身安全等理由，發出證書指示相關訴訟毋須在有陪審團的情況下進行審理。凡律政司長發出上述證書，高等法院原訟法庭應當在沒有陪審團的情況下進行審理，並由三名法官組成審判庭。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">凡律政司長發出前款規定的證書，適用於相關訴訟的香港特別行政區任何法律條文關於 &ldquo;陪審團&rdquo; 或者 &ldquo;陪審團的裁決&rdquo;，均應當理解為指法官或者法官作為事實裁斷者的職能。</em></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7f8cae83d8b80b9f62247e2d373c224ae53d7543","tid":2096511,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:19:06.000Z","msg":"有啲案唔上高院要放區院，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">熱狗你係唔明定扮唔明呃鬼食豆腐呀？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>區域法院處理由裁判法院移交的公訴罪行。公訴罪行是可循公訴程序審訊的刑事罪行，由法官單獨或會同陪審團審理。<span style=\"color: red;\">區域法院法官則在沒有陪審團的情況下單獨進行審訊。</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"44e2ea2ee3a8e1cd3f77c7e7d4840ed3acbc6bf3","tid":2096511,"uid":7439,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:20:29.000Z","msg":"2020仲信OMDB有險可守嗰啲，會唔會投你熱狗啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"ba35d088aa08541febd8c4ba78326676b3d30ed3","tid":2096511,"uid":82720,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"44e2ea2ee3a8e1cd3f77c7e7d4840ed3acbc6bf3","tid":2096511,"uid":7439,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:20:29.000Z","msg":"2020仲信OMDB有險可守嗰啲，會唔會投你熱狗啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:34:21.000Z","msg":"熱狗：法治已死，但我呢下救得翻生！"},{"pid":"f1cfdfa3858378d1c7b6abe20703a38e40ff5714","tid":2096511,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba35d088aa08541febd8c4ba78326676b3d30ed3","tid":2096511,"uid":82720,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"44e2ea2ee3a8e1cd3f77c7e7d4840ed3acbc6bf3","tid":2096511,"uid":7439,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:20:29.000Z","msg":"2020仲信OMDB有險可守嗰啲，會唔會投你熱狗啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:34:21.000Z","msg":"熱狗：法治已死，但我呢下救得翻生！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:01:40.000Z","msg":"永瀆基本法2020"},{"pid":"04b74ff55150f8a6694f372db92bd93a7711521b","tid":2096511,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1cfdfa3858378d1c7b6abe20703a38e40ff5